# SEO & accessibility

Full checklist: `docs/static-site-standards.md` (SEO, Accessibility).

## SEO

- Unique title + meta description per page; canonical URL
- Valid Open Graph + Twitter Card tags; absolute OG image URL (1200×630)
- JSON-LD appropriate types; keep `sitemap.xml` / `robots.txt` in sync when adding routes
- Clean URLs: folder + `index.html` (e.g. `/about/`); hreflang if multilingual

## Accessibility (WCAG 2.2 AA target)

- Semantic HTML first; ARIA only when semantics are insufficient
- Landmarks + skip link; logical heading order
- `aria-label` / `aria-labelledby` / `aria-describedby` on controls; `aria-expanded`, `aria-live`, `aria-hidden` as needed
- All images: meaningful `alt` or `alt=""` if decorative
- Keyboard: full operability; sensible `tabindex` (avoid positive tabindex)
- Contrast AA; `:focus-visible` styles in CSS
- `prefers-reduced-motion` honored in CSS/JS
- Icon-only buttons: `aria-label`; decorative icons: `aria-hidden="true"`

## Verification (human / CI)

- axe, WAVE, Rich Results Test, Schema Markup Validator after major changes
